            <p class="text-white font-content text-lg leading-[32.4px]">Notre mission est de créer des ponts entre les citoyens, les associations,
            et les mairies pour valoriser et dynamiser la vie culturelle de chaque ville.</p>
            <button class="place-self-center bg-cta px-[45px] py-[14px] mt-16 rounded-full text-sm font-cta">Nous rejoindre</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-primary rounded-3xl h-[481px] w-full absolute top-[600px] sm:top-[878px] z-0"></div>
    
    <div class="relative flex flex-col mt-[-90px] z-10">
        <h2 class="text-white font-title text-xl lg:text-4xl place-self-center py-[52px] px-[45px]">
            pourquoi nous rejoindre ?
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 place-self-center mt-8 gap-20 pb-[52px] px-[45px]">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl flex flex-col">
